        <h3 class="project-header">What's your experience?<br></h3>
        <p class="project-body">User personas echoed the results of the user surveys, but Alex indicated that he still liked to use digital retail apps & sites as a “look book” for styles. Brigid wanted the in-store try on to be optimized, as it can be frustrating to bring items into the fitting room only to have to get re-dressed to get additional sizes & styles.<br><br></p>
