          <h3 class="project-subtitle-uniqlo">1. Browse & Send<br></h3>
          <p class="project-body">Browse a curated collection of styles and add items to your digital fitting room. Send the styles to your local Uniqlo to pick up and try on.<br><br></p>
          <h3 class="project-subtitle-uniqlo">2. Pick Up & Try On<br></h3>
          <p class="project-body">Visit your local Uniqlo to pick up your Smart Bag and items to try on. Use the Smart Mirror to request additional sizes or styles.<br><br></p>
          <h3 class="project-subtitle-uniqlo">3. Grab & Go<br></h3>
          <p class="project-body">Fill your Smart Bag with the items that you’d like to keep. Walk out of the store with your Smart Bag and you will automatically be charged for your items. No lines. No wait.<br><br></p>
