        <div class="uniqlo-story-D">
          <div class="uniqlo-story-1-image-send">
            <img src="images/uniqlo_story_send.jpg" class="uniqlo-story-1-image-send-size"></img>
          </div>
          <div class="uniqlo-story-1-text-send">
            <h3 class="project-subtitle">When is good for you?<br></h3>
            <p class="project-body">Once items have been placed in the digital Fitting Room, the user can select additional sizes or colors to try on. The user then sets up a date for their items to be picked up at their local Uniqlo. Once a date is selected, a chart of popular times is displayed to help the user decide on an optimal time to arrive. The user sends the items to the store and is given a success message with a Pick Up Bin number and an option to receive an alert when ready.</p>
