            <h3 class="uniqlo-story-header"><span class="uniqlo-story-header-bold">2 </span>Pick Up<br>& Try On<br></h3>
            <h3 class="project-subtitle">Welcome to your Uniqlo<br></h3>
            <p class="project-body-highlight">After receiving a reminder alert, the user heads to their local Uniqlo to pick up and try on their items. Once the user enters the store, they are reminded to head to the U Concierge to pick up their items and Smart Bag (for first time users).<br><br><br></p>
