            <h3 class="project-subtitle">U Concierge<br></h3>
            <p class="project-body-highlight">Once the user enters the store, an alert reminds them to head to the U Concierge. The U Concierge is the dedicated retail space for U by Uniqlo. It contains the Pick Up bins, the U by Uniqlo Fitting Rooms and the Smart Bag pickup. First time users will be prompted to link their new Smart Bag to expedite check out.<br><br></p>
            <h3 class="project-subtitle">Unlock Your Styles<br></h3>
            <p class="project-body">After the Smart Bag is set up, the user is presented with their Bin Number along with a swiping action to unlock the bin.<br><br></p>
            <h3 class="project-subtitle">Find Your Room<br></h3>
            <p class="project-body">After collecing their items, the user is directed to a specific Fitting Room. The user is presented with another swiping action to unlock their Fitting Room.<br><br></p>
            <h3 class="project-subtitle">Smart Bag<br></h3>
            <p class="project-body">After unlocking the Fitting Room, the user is sent to their Smart Bag with a prompt on how to use it.<br><br></p>
          </div>
