        <div class="uniqlo-story-H">
          <div class="uniqlo-story-2-image-fitting">
            <img src="images/uniqlo_story_fitting.jpg" class="uniqlo-story-2-image-fitting-size"></img>
          </div>
          <div class="uniqlo-story-2-text-fitting">
            <h3 class="project-subtitle">Try Your Styles<br></h3>
            <p class="project-body-highlight">The U by Uniqlo Fitting Rooms are enhanced Fitting Rooms complete with a locking door and Smart Mirror.<br><br></p>
            <h3 class="project-subtitle">Photo Op<br></h3>
            <p class="project-body">The curved back wall of the Fitting Room and a corner mounted phone mount allow users to take optimal “style selfies”. Future versions of U by Uniqlo could include social sharing to get real-time outfit feedback.<br></p>
          </div>
        </div>
