            <h3 class="uniqlo-story-header"><span class="uniqlo-story-header-bold">3 </span>Grab & Go<br></h3>
            <p class="project-body-highlight">After linking their Smart Bag and adding payment information, the user places their selected items into their Smart Bag. Using RFID technology, the Smart Bag recognizes the contents of the bag and creates a digital shopping cart. The user can continue to browse and add items to their Smart Bag.<br><br></p>
