            <p class="project-body-highlight">Once the user is ready to check out, they can simply exit the store. Once the user has exited the store, their payment is processed and the user receives an alert to view the receipt if so desired. Once the transaction is complete, the interface returns to the Style Recommendations with fresh styles for the user to browse.<br><br></p>
